headline: IDEXX Laboratories Elects Joseph L. (Jay) Hooley to Board of Directors
summary: WESTBROOK, Maine, July 10, 2025--IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (NASDAQ: IDXX), a global leader in pet healthcare innovation, today announced the election of Joseph L. (Jay) Hooley to the Company's Board of Directors, effective July 10, 2025.
